
.ad l

.ll 72

.ce 1000
\fBcursor.next()\fR
.ce 0

.sp 2

.SH "NAME"
\fBNAME\fR
.sp 2
next - Return the next record in current cursor.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
\fBSYNOPSIS\fR
.sp 2

.sp 2

.sp 2
cursor.next()
.SH "CATEGORY"
\fBCATEGORY\fR
.sp 2

.sp 2
Cursor
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBDESCRIPTION\fR
.sp 2
Return the next record in current cursor.
.SH "Examples"
\fBExamples\fR
.sp 2
Select records with the value of "age" greater than 10 in the
collection "bar" and return the next record in current cursor.
.sp 2
db.foo.bar.find({age:{$gt:10}}).next()
.sp 2
\fBRelated information\fR
.br
cursor.current()
.br
db.collectionspace.collection.find()